item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

Full music tab. I had to split into two posts, so be sure to read second!

Declare:

public String nothing = "";

In public void initialize, under refreshSkills, put:

		activateTab();

And still, in initialize replace your old music tab with this:

		setSidebarInterface(13, 962); // music tab

And then simply add these somewhere:

[code] public void activateTab() {
loadMusicTab0();
loadMusicTab1();
loadMusicTab2();
loadMusicTab3();
loadMusicTab4();
loadMusicTab5();
loadMusicTab6();
loadMusicTab7();
loadMusicTab8();
}
